(2152, 1, '2014-10-26 17:05:01', '2014-10-26 17:05:01', 'Prizes are awarded annually by the editors of <span class="afrikana">The Afrikana Review</span>. Winning selections are announced in the winter issue. No application form is required; winners are selected from the stories and poems published in <span class="afrikana">The Afrikana Review</span> each year.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review Story Award (Ages 13-16)</h1>\r\nThe Afrikana Review Story Award (13-16) is awarded to the story with targeting teens, ages 13-16, of any genre. The winner receives a $1,000 prize and a hand-crafted trophy.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review Story Award (Ages 16-19)</h1>\r\nThe Afrikana Review Story Award (16-19) is awarded to the story with targeting teens, ages 16-19, of any genre. The winner receives a $1,000 prize and a hand-crafted trophy.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review Theme Award</h1>\r\nThe Afrikana Theme Award is awarded to the author whose story was the best of all the themed stories. The winner receives a $1,000 prize and a hand-crafted trophy.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review for Rising Writers Award</h1>\r\nThe Afrikana Review for Rising Writers is award to writers 19 and under who demonstrates the talent and drive to become the next great Black author for Young Adult. The winner will also serve on the prestigious panel of judges for The Afrikana Review Prize of 2016, bringing a critical young perspective to the evaluation process. Entrants must submit a Rising Writer Personal Profile of 700 characters. Those that do not will only be considered for the individual story award of their targeted audience.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review Poetry Award</h1>\r\n>The Afrikana Review Poetry Award is awarded to the poet whose poem engages with the unfamiliar and provokes emotion. The winner receives a $1,000 prize and a hand-crafted trophy.\r\n\r\n<h1>The Afrikana Review Criticism Award</h1>\r\nThe Afrikana Review Non-Fiction Award is awarded to the writer whose study, evaluation, or interpretation of literature ', '<i class="prizes-icon fa fa-trophy"></i> Prizes <i class="fa fa-trophy"></i>', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'prizes', '', '', '2014-11-06 07:24:05', '2014-11-06 07:24:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=2152', 0, 'page', '', 0),
